item.title: CVE-2018-1407|2024-08-05T03:59:39.104Z -- ibm -- rational%20team%20concert
item.description: IBM Rational Team Concert 5.0 through 5.0.2 and 6.0 through 6.0.5 are vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 138445.
